1557
00:42:17,699 --> 00:42:18,139
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1558
00:42:18,139 --> 00:42:20,679
[SPEAKER_01] ono preuzetno doživljavanje božanske providnosti.

1559
00:42:20,679 --> 00:42:21,059
