1594
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:22,199
[SPEAKER_01] nego ne.

1595
00:43:22,199 --> 00:43:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] Netko koji je bio ili prije,

1596
00:43:24,019 --> 00:43:25,400
