1597
00:43:25,400 --> 00:43:26,139
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne znam kada,

1598
00:43:26,139 --> 00:43:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću podkopavati njegov autoriteti

1599
00:43:28,199 --> 00:43:29,739
