1610
00:43:48,340 --> 00:43:50,079
[SPEAKER_01] Kako god hoćete hierarhijski.

1611
00:43:50,659 --> 00:43:52,480
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, riječ je o narcisojnoj osobi.

1612
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:53,739
