1623
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] Meni sa jednog slušajer sam ja i zabran.

1624
00:44:16,480 --> 00:44:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] Zato su moje odluke jedine odraz Božje volje.

1625
00:44:20,199 --> 00:44:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1626
00:44:21,719 --> 00:44:24,280
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, i to ovako.

1627
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:27,559
