1629
00:44:30,800 --> 00:44:32,840
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo, kako se izražava?

1630
00:44:32,840 --> 00:44:39,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se potisnuta muškost želi, dakle, ispoljeti.

1631
00:44:39,019 --> 00:44:41,420
