1632
00:44:41,420 --> 00:44:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, narcisoidost postaje agresija.

1633
00:44:43,980 --> 00:44:47,579
[SPEAKER_01] A agresija je upravo to, potisnuta muškost.

1634
00:44:47,579 --> 00:44:49,420
