1641
00:45:02,840 --> 00:45:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je depresivan.

1642
00:45:03,800 --> 00:45:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ali negdje je puklo, bilo vani, to je agresija,

1643
00:45:06,980 --> 00:45:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] bilo unutra, depresija.

1644
00:45:08,440 --> 00:45:11,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, a kompleks mučeništva,

1645
00:45:11,820 --> 00:45:15,420
