1648
00:45:20,860 --> 00:45:23,059
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, taj je komplek žrtve i tako dalje.

1649
00:45:23,139 --> 00:45:24,699
[SPEAKER_01] onda pokušava na taj način.

1650
00:45:24,699 --> 00:45:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo, opravdati ono kad je nekoga prokazao.

1651
00:45:28,260 --> 00:45:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, znači to je to, vlastne autoritete,

1652
00:45:31,039 --> 00:45:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] menja na potkopavanju tuđeg autoriteta.

1653
00:45:33,699 --> 00:45:36,139
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo, objasnio sam aktivno,

1654
00:45:36,139 --> 00:45:38,780
[SPEAKER_01] a pogledajte kako pasivno se može potkopavati.

1655
00:45:39,699 --> 00:45:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] Na primjer, kada pita za savjet autoritet,

1656
00:45:43,539 --> 00:45:44,940
[SPEAKER_01] ali to ne odradi.

1657
00:45:44,940 --> 00:45:48,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je pasivno potkopavanje.

1658
00:45:48,900 --> 00:45:50,139
[SPEAKER_01] Na primjer, ok,

1659
00:45:50,139 --> 00:45:53,599
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ono aktivno je baš javno govore

1660
00:45:53,599 --> 00:45:54,719
[SPEAKER_01] protiv nekoga ovo ono.

1661
00:45:54,719 --> 00:45:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] A pasivno daću taj primjer.

1662
00:45:56,380 --> 00:45:58,880
[SPEAKER_01] Na primjer, autoritet pita za neki savjet,

1663
00:45:58,880 --> 00:46:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja pitam autoritet za neki savjet,

1664
00:46:01,099 --> 00:46:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali ga neću slušati.

1665
00:46:02,539 --> 00:46:04,139
[SPEAKER_01] Nego, što ću još napraviti?

1666
00:46:04,139 --> 00:46:09,019
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, taj savjet i tu zapovjed,

1667
00:46:09,139 --> 00:46:11,079
[SPEAKER_01] taj nalog koji mi je dao moj autoritet,

1668
00:46:11,079 --> 00:46:12,699
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću komentirati s drugima.

1669
00:46:12,699 --> 00:46:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako reći ću kako ja mislim

1670
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:16,820
[SPEAKER_01] da to nije bilo dobro,

1671
00:46:16,820 --> 00:46:19,480
[SPEAKER_01] ja mi znači da taj savjet nije bio na mojoj izgranju,

1672
00:46:19,480 --> 00:46:21,739
[SPEAKER_01] pa reci to autoritetu koji ti je dao savjet.

1673
00:46:21,739 --> 00:46:23,099
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto imaš svoj krug ljudi

1674
00:46:23,099 --> 00:46:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] s kojim to moraš...

1675
00:46:23,920 --> 00:46:26,039
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je pasivno potkopavanje autoriteta.

1676
00:46:26,039 --> 00:46:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] Sveti Josip nema problema s time.

1677
00:46:29,420 --> 00:46:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] Gledajte jednu stvar.

1678
00:46:30,739 --> 00:46:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Sveti Josip je kraljevske časti.

1679
00:46:33,159 --> 00:46:35,780
[SPEAKER_01] I on nema potkopavanje autoriteta

1680
00:46:35,780 --> 00:46:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu, on ide u hram, sluša zakon,

1681
00:46:38,079 --> 00:46:39,739
[SPEAKER_01] sluša farizeje.

1682
00:46:39,739 --> 00:46:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] On je mogao reći, ovo je Sid Boži,

1683
00:46:41,619 --> 00:46:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] meni je došao Anđeo Gospodnji.

1684
00:46:42,960 --> 00:46:45,179
[SPEAKER_01] Što ćemo mi sada se podlagati

1685
00:46:45,179 --> 00:46:46,739
[SPEAKER_01] nekom starom zakonu židovskom?

1686
00:46:47,119 --> 00:46:48,659
[SPEAKER_01] Nije ću ja ću njega ubriti za tu hramu.

1687
00:46:48,659 --> 00:46:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je došao Anđeo Gospodnji,

1688
00:46:50,119 --> 00:46:51,179
[SPEAKER_01] to je sigurno Sid Boži.

1689
00:46:51,179 --> 00:46:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ili, na primjer,

1690
00:46:52,880 --> 00:46:54,519
[SPEAKER_01] car Augusta ili kralj Herod.

1691
00:46:54,519 --> 00:46:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ma nikakve riječi protiv njih.

1692
00:46:56,940 --> 00:46:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] On se podlaže

1693
00:46:58,519 --> 00:47:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] tadašnjim autoritetu.

1694
00:47:00,300 --> 00:47:02,159
[SPEAKER_01] Propisu cara Augusta

1695
00:47:02,159 --> 00:47:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] i kralju Herodu.

1696
00:47:03,840 --> 00:47:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako.

1697
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:05,179
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1698
00:47:05,179 --> 00:47:07,219
[SPEAKER_01] Kakav god bi autoritet,

1699
00:47:07,219 --> 00:47:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] taj autoritet je tako da,

1700
00:47:09,460 --> 00:47:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] ne trebaš se s njime složiti,

1701
00:47:10,760 --> 00:47:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali nemoj ga, dakle,

1702
00:47:12,500 --> 00:47:14,639
[SPEAKER_01] aktivno ili pasivno potkopavati.

1703
00:47:14,639 --> 00:47:15,440
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to vidimo.

1704
00:47:15,440 --> 00:47:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to jednače, ono,

1705
00:47:16,699 --> 00:47:17,699
[SPEAKER_01] baš narcisoidno.

1706
00:47:17,699 --> 00:47:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

1707
00:47:18,039 --> 00:47:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, i ono,

1708
00:47:20,079 --> 00:47:21,260
[SPEAKER_01] kada dobiveni savjet,

1709
00:47:21,260 --> 00:47:23,179
[SPEAKER_01] okrećeš protiv samog autoriteta.

1710
00:47:23,179 --> 00:47:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] To je ona igra.

1711
00:47:24,679 --> 00:47:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, a zašto?

1712
00:47:26,179 --> 00:47:28,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to ste mi vi savjetovali tako.

1713
00:47:28,019 --> 00:47:29,780
[SPEAKER_01] Što je, u čemu je sad problem?

1714
00:47:29,780 --> 00:47:30,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

1715
00:47:30,519 --> 00:47:33,019
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, imamo još dvije stvari.

1716
00:47:33,019 --> 00:47:34,539
[SPEAKER_01] Lažna podiznost.

1717
00:47:34,539 --> 00:47:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] To smo čuvali sto puta.

1718
00:47:36,619 --> 00:47:38,219
[SPEAKER_01] Konkretno kako izgleda

1719
00:47:38,219 --> 00:47:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] muška lažna podiznost?

1720
00:47:39,460 --> 00:47:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] Baš ono, muška lažna podiznost.

1721
00:47:41,079 --> 00:47:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovako.

1722
00:47:44,639 --> 00:47:46,699
[SPEAKER_01] Lažna podiznost,

1723
00:47:46,699 --> 00:47:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] prije svega što je podiznost?

1724
00:47:48,400 --> 00:47:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] Podiznost je, dakle,

1725
00:47:49,699 --> 00:47:51,760
[SPEAKER_01] govoriti ili malo

1726
00:47:51,760 --> 00:47:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] ili uopće ne govoriti o sebi.

1727
00:47:53,239 --> 00:47:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je podiznost.

1728
00:47:54,460 --> 00:47:55,460
[SPEAKER_01] Tu je sveti osip,

1729
00:47:55,460 --> 00:47:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] naravno, prvi pretljači,

1730
00:47:56,559 --> 00:47:57,019
[SPEAKER_01] jel' tako?

1731
00:47:57,019 --> 00:47:58,360
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je podiznost.

1732
00:47:58,360 --> 00:48:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Govoriti o sebi malo,

1733
00:48:00,699 --> 00:48:01,880
[SPEAKER_01] kada mi se nešto pita,

1734
00:48:01,880 --> 00:48:03,519
[SPEAKER_01] ili uopće ne govoriti o sebi.

1735
00:48:04,219 --> 00:48:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] Kako onda izgleda lažna podiznost?

1736
00:48:05,719 --> 00:48:08,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ako dosta govori o sebi,

1737
00:48:08,260 --> 00:48:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] čak i o ne negativnosti,

1738
00:48:09,860 --> 00:48:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] najčešće negativnosti,

1739
00:48:11,380 --> 00:48:12,280
[SPEAKER_01] ali govoriš o sebi.

1740
00:48:12,280 --> 00:48:15,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dijeli svoju intimu,

1741
00:48:15,380 --> 00:48:17,400
[SPEAKER_01] svi živi znaju kakvih je problema

1742
00:48:17,400 --> 00:48:19,199
[SPEAKER_01] ima s mamom, ima s tatom,

1743
00:48:19,199 --> 00:48:20,719
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo duhovnik te osobe,

1744
00:48:20,719 --> 00:48:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] nego svi, svi živi.

1745
00:48:23,440 --> 00:48:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] svoje rane,

1746
00:48:24,300 --> 00:48:26,440
[SPEAKER_01] razglavio i objašnjava s drugima

1747
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] ili s mnogima.

1748
00:48:27,639 --> 00:48:29,400
[SPEAKER_01] Puno govori o svom životu

1749
00:48:29,400 --> 00:48:30,780
[SPEAKER_01] prije obraćenja, na primjer.

1750
00:48:30,780 --> 00:48:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] Jako voli svoj život.

1751
00:48:31,900 --> 00:48:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] Jako govori pričati o sebi,

1752
00:48:33,360 --> 00:48:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] kakav sam ja bio kao stari čovjek,

1753
00:48:35,440 --> 00:48:36,940
[SPEAKER_01] kakav sam ja bio u prošlom.

1754
00:48:36,940 --> 00:48:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] Jako, mislim, jedno je svijedočiti

1755
00:48:39,300 --> 00:48:41,019
[SPEAKER_01] jedan put kad mi se nešto pita.

1756
00:48:41,019 --> 00:48:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] Govoriti cijelo vrijeme,

1757
00:48:42,119 --> 00:48:43,719
[SPEAKER_01] to je već malo narcisoidno,

1758
00:48:43,719 --> 00:48:45,900
[SPEAKER_01] ta fiksacija na stari,

1759
00:48:45,900 --> 00:48:47,079
[SPEAKER_01] prošli, grešli život.

1760
00:48:47,079 --> 00:48:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogo se ponižava,

1761
00:48:49,619 --> 00:48:51,280
[SPEAKER_01] baš ono, ponižavanje,

1762
00:48:51,920 --> 00:48:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] ili aktivno se skriva

1763
00:48:53,960 --> 00:48:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] iza drugih članova.

1764
00:48:55,539 --> 00:48:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo to tako reći.

1765
00:48:56,500 --> 00:48:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, recimo,

1766
00:48:58,579 --> 00:49:00,260
[SPEAKER_01] pridavanje,

1767
00:49:00,260 --> 00:49:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se još tu vidi?

1768
00:49:01,099 --> 00:49:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pridavanje, recimo,

1769
00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] važnosti svjedočanstvima

1770
00:49:04,460 --> 00:49:06,860
[SPEAKER_01] kao jedinom sredstvu evangelizacije.

1771
00:49:06,860 --> 00:49:09,360
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino kad neko svjedoči,

1772
00:49:09,360 --> 00:49:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] to najbolje obraća druge ljude.

1773
00:49:10,940 --> 00:49:12,519
[SPEAKER_01] To najbolje približava gospodinu.

1774
00:49:12,519 --> 00:49:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svjedočanstvo je važno.

1775
00:49:14,000 --> 00:49:15,340
[SPEAKER_01] Važno je čuti svjedočanstve.

1776
00:49:15,340 --> 00:49:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] I vi ih ovdje slušate.

1777
00:49:16,280 --> 00:49:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ali pridavati tome važnost

1778
00:49:18,019 --> 00:49:19,880
[SPEAKER_01] kao jedinom, pravom,

1779
00:49:20,260 --> 00:49:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] najboljem, autentičnom izvoru,

1780
00:49:22,500 --> 00:49:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno sredstvu evangelizacije,

1781
00:49:24,000 --> 00:49:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] to je problem.

1782
00:49:24,659 --> 00:49:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] To bude problem.

1783
00:49:26,079 --> 00:49:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] I sakramentu ispovjedi

1784
00:49:29,500 --> 00:49:31,559
[SPEAKER_01] kao jedinom izvoru milosti.

1785
00:49:31,559 --> 00:49:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] Vi znate,

1786
00:49:32,480 --> 00:49:34,780
[SPEAKER_01] Bog nam je dao mnogih sakramenata

1787
00:49:34,780 --> 00:49:36,320
[SPEAKER_01] i mnogih drugih izvora milosti.

1788
00:49:36,320 --> 00:49:38,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ali naglašavanje baš sakramenta

1789
00:49:38,340 --> 00:49:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] ispovjedi kao jedinom izvoru milosti.

1790
00:49:40,380 --> 00:49:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1791
00:49:40,800 --> 00:49:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] Jer tamo opet može pričati o sebi.

1792
00:49:42,380 --> 00:49:44,639
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je isto ispovjednje mogućnost,

1793
00:49:45,000 --> 00:49:46,599
[SPEAKER_01] gdje opet može pričati o sebi.

1794
00:49:46,599 --> 00:49:47,099
[SPEAKER_01] Je li tako?

1795
00:49:47,099 --> 00:49:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] I na kraju

1796
00:49:49,239 --> 00:49:51,699
[SPEAKER_01] je neempatičnost.

1797
00:49:51,699 --> 00:49:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, što to znači

1798
00:49:53,800 --> 00:49:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] kako vjernik može biti neempatičan?

1799
00:49:56,519 --> 00:49:57,239
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1800
00:49:58,119 --> 00:49:59,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ipak, ono, to je naše poslanje.

1801
00:49:59,699 --> 00:50:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] Biti tu za druge,

1802
00:50:00,539 --> 00:50:01,719
[SPEAKER_01] biti altruističan,

1803
00:50:01,719 --> 00:50:03,559
[SPEAKER_01] slušati potrebe drugih itd.

1804
00:50:03,559 --> 00:50:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, narcisojeni vjernik

1805
00:50:06,420 --> 00:50:08,739
[SPEAKER_01] će slušati.

1806
00:50:08,739 --> 00:50:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] On će izgledati sučutno

1807
00:50:10,460 --> 00:50:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] i slušat će o patnjama,

1808
00:50:12,500 --> 00:50:14,199
[SPEAKER_01] o bolima, o problemima drugih.

1809
00:50:14,199 --> 00:50:16,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne zato što ga zanimaju

1810
00:50:16,059 --> 00:50:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] ti osjećaji drugoga,

1811
00:50:18,039 --> 00:50:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] nego zato što ga zanimaju

1812
00:50:20,239 --> 00:50:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] osjećaji koji su vezane

1813
00:50:22,159 --> 00:50:23,260
[SPEAKER_01] uz njega samoga.

1814
00:50:23,260 --> 00:50:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, samo takvi osjećaji ga zanimaju.

1815
00:50:26,280 --> 00:50:27,199
[SPEAKER_01] Od druge osobe.

1816
00:50:27,780 --> 00:50:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, on je empatičan

1817
00:50:28,960 --> 00:50:31,300
[SPEAKER_01] jedino kad su osjećaji druge osobe

1818
00:50:31,300 --> 00:50:32,679
[SPEAKER_01] vezane uz mene.

1819
00:50:32,679 --> 00:50:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] Vezane uz mene samoga.

1820
00:50:34,119 --> 00:50:34,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1821
00:50:34,539 --> 00:50:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo da su pozitivi ali negativni?

1822
00:50:36,179 --> 00:50:36,840
[SPEAKER_01] Želim znati.

1823
00:50:36,840 --> 00:50:38,699
[SPEAKER_01] Želim znati kako se ti osjećaš.

1824
00:50:38,699 --> 00:50:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ti je osjećaje dajem.

1825
00:50:40,059 --> 00:50:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] Što?

1826
00:50:40,500 --> 00:50:41,159
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje.

1827
00:50:41,159 --> 00:50:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1828
00:50:41,340 --> 00:50:43,820
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno, u toj neempatičnosti

1829
00:50:43,820 --> 00:50:45,840
[SPEAKER_01] može doći do manipulacije savješću.

1830
00:50:45,840 --> 00:50:46,679
[SPEAKER_01] Jel tako?

1831
00:50:46,679 --> 00:50:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] I istaknuti prozelitizam.

1832
00:50:50,400 --> 00:50:51,500
[SPEAKER_01] Što znači istaknuti?

1833
00:50:51,500 --> 00:50:52,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači što je prozelitizam?

1834
00:50:52,699 --> 00:50:54,199
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, da govarati nekoga,

1835
00:50:54,579 --> 00:50:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći na vjeru, ono, huškati,

1836
00:50:56,500 --> 00:50:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] baš ono negativni izraz,

1837
00:50:57,539 --> 00:50:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] nekoga na vjeru.

1838
00:50:59,199 --> 00:50:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1839
00:50:59,380 --> 00:51:00,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, agresivno,

1840
00:51:00,340 --> 00:51:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] agresivno obraćenje,

1841
00:51:02,500 --> 00:51:04,139
[SPEAKER_01] obraćenje nekoga i tako dalje.

1842
00:51:04,139 --> 00:51:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1843
00:51:04,320 --> 00:51:05,679
[SPEAKER_01] I to je baš ono istaknuto

1844
00:51:05,679 --> 00:51:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] kod narcisojnih vjernika.

1845
00:51:07,840 --> 00:51:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] I kod manipulacije savješću,

1846
00:51:10,199 --> 00:51:11,539
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, pogotovo ako je

1847
00:51:11,539 --> 00:51:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] duhovnik narcisojda,

1848
00:51:13,340 --> 00:51:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] nažalost,

1849
00:51:14,059 --> 00:51:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] onda to ovako izgleda.

1850
00:51:15,420 --> 00:51:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] No stop

1851
00:51:16,599 --> 00:51:18,099
[SPEAKER_01] pocijećanje

1852
00:51:18,099 --> 00:51:20,739
[SPEAKER_01] na grešnu prošlost neke osobe.

1853
00:51:20,739 --> 00:51:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ti tu osobu no stop pocijećanje.

1854
00:51:22,739 --> 00:51:23,739
